code: public static final String documentId(String jobId, int docNum) {     return documentPrefix(jobId) + docNum. }
public static final String documentPrefix(String jobId) {     return jobId + "_" + TYPE + "#". }

code: /**  * This is how the IDs were formed in v5.4  */ public static final String v54DocumentId(String jobId, int docNum) {     return v54DocumentPrefix(jobId) + docNum. }
public static final String v54DocumentPrefix(String jobId) {     return jobId + "#". }

comment: /**  * Given the id of a categorizer state document it extracts the job id  * @param docId the categorizer state document id  * @return the job id or {@code null} if the id is not valid  */
code: /**  * Given the id of a categorizer state document it extracts the job id  * @param docId the categorizer state document id  * @return the job id or {@code null} if the id is not valid  */ public static final String extractJobId(String docId) {     int suffixIndex = docId.lastIndexOf("_" + TYPE).     return suffixIndex <= 0 ? null : docId.substring(0, suffixIndex). }
